<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to <%= app_name %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f7;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #C563FF;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .credentials-container {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #C563FF;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .credentials-container p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .credentials-container span {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #C563FF;
        }

        .next-steps {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .next-steps p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .next-steps ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .next-steps ul li {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #C563FF;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">

        <% if (logo_url) { %>
            <img src="<%= logo_url %>" alt="<%= app_name %> Logo" class="logo">
        <% } %>

        <h1>Welcome to <%= app_name %>! 🎉</h1>

        <p class="greeting">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>Your account has been created successfully. Here are your login credentials to get started:</p>

        <div class="credentials-container">
            <p>📧 Email &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span><%= email %></span></p>
            <p>🔑 Password &nbsp; <span><%= password %></span></p>
        </div>

        <p class="notice">For your security, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <p>Here's what you can do next:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Log in to your account and explore the dashboard</li>
                <li>Complete your profile by adding your phone number</li>
                <li>Change your password to something memorable</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= login_url %>" class="btn">Login to Your Account</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need help, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

        <p>Welcome aboard,<br>The <%= app_name %> Team</p>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= app_name %>. All rights reserved.
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>
